Fractal demo

Overview

This is a demo app of Fractal, using the Nunjucks adapter and the default Mandelbrot theme (with custom colors though).

The components showcased are purely fictional and were created solely for the demonstration. They have been made using Tailwind CSS, bundled with Webpack.

Browse the code of this demo on Github to learn more.

Thank you

  • to Netlify for the hosting
  • to unDraw for the illustrations
  • to Unsplash for the pictures
  • to Heroicons for the icons
